{"tid":2119603,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"上半年23警無力還債 1人欠債長達15年","createTime":"2020-07-22T07:52:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T08:14:33.000Z","uid":240362,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b5ed4fbe2e4781ed4513fa96ca7a9d9f95eb6942","tid":2119603,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:52:01.000Z","msg":"保安局向立法會提交文件顯示，截至今年6月30日，有23名警務人員無力償還債項，其中一人自2005年下半年起開始負債，長達15年，亦有7人至少負債5年以上。餘下15人是自2016年上半年起開始負債，包括去年下半年有3人及今年上半年有1人。<br />\n<br />\n文件顯示，共有23名警務人員無力償還債項，為近年最低。2019年同期則有27人，2018年及2017年上半年人數分別有36和37人。<br />\n<br />\n至於負債原因，17名負債警員指是「家人和親友的問題」，因為「重要人生大事」有5人，而「賭博」致負債則有1人。當局於今年上半年仍未有發出任何「追討稅款通知書」，而2019年同期曾發出18張。"},{"pid":"40f5d1712fb1b74953afde7839aaeff2d6ff7d7c","tid":2119603,"uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:52:59.000Z","msg":"17名負債警員指是「家人和親友的問題」，因為「重要人生大事」有5人，而「賭博」致負債則有1人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de46048a20897ded80c0e0872cf2b7f2b5fc0e2","tid":2119603,"uid":137038,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:53:23.000Z","msg":"咁多OT錢都還唔到？賭幾大呀？"},{"pid":"77c14151f91a292b9ab873e7e70c193b3ebc781a","tid":2119603,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5de46048a20897ded80c0e0872cf2b7f2b5fc0e2","tid":2119603,"uid":137038,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:53:23.000Z","msg":"咁多OT錢都還唔到？賭幾大呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:53:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmo